metadata.name: Celestial Shore
metadata.description:
In middle of the sand far the lights top in building and sea shore, I grab my mobile and used my senses to capture what I think differently! Took a moment then high speeding in process and enjoyed taking a different moment over the place.
 
Clicked - Mobile
Process/Method - Intentional Camera Movement
Place - World's Second Longest Beach (Marina Beach ,Chennai ,Tamil Nadu)

Captured by Kamlesh DK

Photography + Express The Capture
 
Owning this capture is giving you my way of expressing the capture in a digital format. ;)
